{"tid":1462074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於阻礙旅客問題","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:45.000Z","uid":2762,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"43adf80f8c8bfad5d3e67db10c2e87f43ad65f7e","tid":1462074,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"今日見好多人鬧阻旅客上機唔啱，我明白觀感上唔好睇，但今日唔似噚日咁多人，噚日人多自然可以塞爆。但人唔多，好難真正癱瘓到機場，變相只可以升級行動，阻一兩個客可能會照飛，但大部分旅客都上唔到，機場必會作出應對。<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣可以唔阻旅客，但又可以癱瘓到機場？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係要夠多人</span><br />\n所以盡量有咁多戈塞咁多人，到時咩都唔使做，自然可以癱瘓到。"},{"pid":"33bee1b6b0c67f4dffb39acf007ba9c7da7cbecd","tid":1462074,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07ced8c58f68d9a34c50185a82287f7818a787dc","tid":1462074,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd6c2b4abcea8a13a91204ee417411c51f242f7c","tid":1462074,"uid":165840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"謝絕破壞，不使用武力!"},{"pid":"482fd44bb41ba4a8b3bcb7901e6ec569ebd09c6e","tid":1462074,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c63fca4488e9fdd50420bd8df9118bbcc36735e","tid":1462074,"uid":111955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"一定係警察做<br />\n尋日分化完唔work<br />\n今日又搵話題發大黎講<br />\n唔好比班狗發大件事，轉移視線<br />\n阻旅客上機係警犬，處理左<br />\n小問題，<br />\n我地返返主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ba4cebe3bb3fa99b8b9318e36c2db6539e9461","tid":1462074,"uid":142204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT